These are Puzzles for 4x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: juice, mirinda, water
3 different pets are kept: rabbit, hedgehog, fish
3 different games are played: scrabble, whist, poker
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: azalea, poppy, begonia
1. the owner of the hedgehog is the person drinking mirinda##1
2. the person who growsbegonia is on the far left##1
3. the person drinking water is on the left of the person who growsazalea##1
4. the person playing scrabble is the owner of the fish##1
5. the owner of the rabbit is in the middle##1
6. the person drinking water is the owner of the fish##1
7. the person playing poker is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |      2      |     3     |
| Beverage      | water  | juice       | mirinda   |
| Pet          | fish | rabbit | hedgehog |
| Game         | scrabble  | poker | whist    |
| Flower   | begonia | azalea       | poppy      |

