.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-2::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: trance, r&b, indie
The people have 3 different hobbies: rock-climbing, singing, traveling
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: superhero, fantasy, comedy
The people use 3 different means of transport: scooter, airplane, bike
1. the fan of trance is on the left of the fan of r&b##1
2. the fan of indie is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person watching fantasy movies##1
4. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
5. the person driving the bike is on the far left##1
6. the person driving the bike is the person watching superhero movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |       3       |
| Music-Genre          | trance      | r&b  | indie        |
| Hobby         | traveling | singing | rock-climbing |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero | fantasy | comedy       |
| Transport           | bike     | airplane     | scooter      |

