.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-3::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, havana, siglo
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: marigold, dahlia, begonia
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: adventure, satire, zombie
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: salsa, pop, disco
1. the person who growsbegonia is the fan of salsa##1
2. the fan of pop is on the right of the bolivar-smoker##1
3. the person who growsdahlia is on the left of the fan of salsa##1
4. the person watching zombie movies is in the middle##1
5. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person who growsbegonia##1
6. the siglo-smoker is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |         2          |    3    |
| Cigar      | havana    | bolivar        | siglo |
| Flower           | dahlia    | begonia | marigold    |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure | zombie             | satire  |
| Music-Genre     | disco     | salsa                | pop  |

