.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-4::.
There 3 different types of food: pear, pepper, tomato
City: miami, paris, colone
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: march, september, april
3 different games are played: chess, monopoly, mah-jongg
1. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
2. the person eating tomato is on the left of the person traveling to paris##1
3. the person playing chess is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
4. the person eating pear is the person playing mah-jongg##1
5. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person traveling to miami##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3     |
| Food          | pepper    | tomato  | pear      |
| City           | colone    | miami | paris |
| Birthday   | april   | september  | march     |
| Game   | chess | monopoly    | mah-jongg      |

