.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-5::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: skateboard, quad-bike, roller
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: april, september, july
City: san-francisco, miami, london
3 different pets are kept: dog, hedgehog, lizard
1. the person traveling to san-francisco is the person who's birthday is in september##1
2. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
3. the person who's birthday is in july is the person driving the roller##1
4. the person driving the roller is on the far left##1
5. the owner of the dog is the person driving the skateboard##1
6. the person traveling to london is the person who's birthday is in april##1
7. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |     3     |
| Transport         | roller | skateboard     | quad-bike   |
| Birthday           | july       | september   | april     |
| City   | miami     | san-francisco | london |
| Pet           | lizard      | dog         | hedgehog  |

