The people prefer 3 different music-genres: gospel, house, indie
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: march, july, february
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: action, scientific, documentary
1. the canadian is on the right of the fan of gospel##1
2. the person who's birthday is in march is in the middle##1
3. the fan of indie is on the far left##1
4. the mexican is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1
5. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |    3    |
| Nationality          | indian | mexican       | canadian |
| Music-Genre   | indie     | gospel       | house   |
| Birthday           | july      | march       | february     |
| Movie-Genre         | action   | scientific | documentary  |

