3 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, game, swisher
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: horror, mystery, spy
The people have 3 different hobbies: board-games, cooking, chess
1. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the far left##1
2. the game-smoker is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
3. the swisher-smoker is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1
4. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
5. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2        |     3      |
| Beverage          | fanta       | juice         | soy-milk   |
| Cigar           | chaman | swisher | game |
| Movie-Genre   | horror     | mystery        | spy        |
| Hobby   | cooking      | board-games           | chess        |

