City: edinburgh, venice, hannover
There 3 different types of food: grapes, pear, grapefruit
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, siglo, dannemann
1. the bongani-smoker is on the far right##1
2. the person eating grapefruit is the dannemann-smoker##1
3. the person who's hobby is woodworking is in the middle##1
4. the person traveling to hannover is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
5. the person eating grapefruit is on the left of the person traveling to venice##1
6. the bongani-smoker is the person eating pear##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3       |
| Hobby         | puzzles   | woodworking | magic-tricks |
| City   | edinburgh | hannover         | venice       |
| Food           | grapes      | grapefruit      | pear         |
| Cigar     | siglo      | dannemann         | bongani          |

