3 different games are played: scrabble, domino, poker
3 different pets are kept: goat, goldfish, guinea-pig
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: april, may, september
1. the person who's birthday is in september is in the middle##1
2. the owner of the goldfish is on the far right##1
3. the havana-smoker is the person who's birthday is in may##1
4. the person playing scrabble is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
5. the person playing poker is on the far left##1
6. the game-smoker is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |         1          |     2      |    3     |
| Cigar       | havana            | bluemaster      | game  |
| Game         | poker | scrabble | domino |
| Pet         | goat               | guinea-pig | goldfish |
| Birthday   | may             | september       | april      |

