The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: epic, martial-arts, mystery
The people use 3 different means of transport: train, car, tram
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: soccer, skateboarding, handball
1. the person watching martial-arts movies is the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
2. the person who's sport is handball is on the far left##1
3. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
4. the person who's birthday is in january is on the far right##1
5. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
6. the person driving the car is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |      3      |
| Birthday           | april | february         | january |
| Movie-Genre   | epic      | martial-arts | mystery     |
| Transport   | train   | car       | tram     |
| Sport           | handball    | skateboarding         | soccer        |

