.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-11::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  architect, journalist, videographer
There are 3 different favourite colors: light-blue, ebony, lavender
There are 3 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, water, lemonade
City: miami, hamburg, boston
1. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the journalist##1
2. the videographer is on the right of the person who likes lavender##1
3. the videographer is on the right of the person traveling to boston##1
4. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
5. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the videographer##1
6. the person who likes ebony is on the left of the person who likes light-blue##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |     3     |
| Job           | journalist | videographer | architect |
| Color   | lavender        | ebony       | light-blue     |
| Beverage   | water     | lemonade         | soy-milk     |
| City     | boston | hamburg          | miami      |

