There are 3 different favourite colors: white, chestnut, lilac
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: folk, gospel, rock
The people have 3 different hobbies: card-games, woodworking, baking
1. the person who's hobby is baking is the fan of gospel##1
2. the person who likes chestnut is on the far left##1
3. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person who likes white##1
4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
5. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the fan of folk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |      3      |
| Birthday      | january    | april | june |
| Color   | chestnut | white     | lilac     |
| Music-Genre   | rock        | gospel        | folk        |
| Hobby           | woodworking    | baking         | card-games     |

