.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-13::.
There 3 different types of food: peach, lettuce, cabbage
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, snowmobile, tram
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: zombie, musical, family
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: badminton, cricket, sailing
1. the person who's sport is sailing is the person eating peach##1
2. the person watching family movies is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1
3. the person eating lettuce is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
4. the person eating cabbage is the person driving the snowmobile##1
5. the person watching family movies is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
6. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |     3     |
| Food         | lettuce | peach | cabbage   |
| Transport           | tram     | car    | snowmobile   |
| Movie-Genre   | musical         | family    | zombie   |
| Sport         | cricket       | sailing | badminton |

