There are 3 different favourite colors: blue, white, purple
1. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
2. the person watching superhero movies is the person who's hobby is collecting##1
3. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the person who likes blue##1
4. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person who growsdaffodil##1
5. the person watching spy movies is the person who likes purple##1
6. the person who likes white is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |     3      |
| Movie-Genre    | western | superhero     | spy      |
| Flower        | azalea | daffodil       | daisy |
| Hobby       | sudoku | collecting | traveling  |
| Color   | white    | blue   | purple  |

