3 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, pall-mall, baccarat
3 different pets are kept: goat, lizard, snake
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: classical, gospel, salsa
1. the fan of classical is on the far right##1
2. the pall-mall-smoker is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
3. the fan of gospel is the owner of the goat##1
4. the owner of the goat is on the far left##1
5. the person traveling to colone is in the middle##1
6. the baccarat-smoker is the person traveling to london##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |     3      |
| City      | london | colone | boston       |
| Cigar          | baccarat     | dannemann   | pall-mall       |
| Pet         | goat  | snake   | lizard |
| Music-Genre   | gospel   | salsa       | classical  |

