.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-17::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: january, june, april
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: golf, skateboarding, snowboarding
The people have 3 different hobbies: chess, baking, rock-climbing
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: d&b, folk, punk
1. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
2. the fan of d&b is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1
3. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the fan of punk##1
4. the fan of folk is on the far right##1
5. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
6. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2    |    3    |
| Birthday      | april      | june    | january    |
| Sport          | snowboarding         | skateboarding    | golf   |
| Hobby           | chess | rock-climbing | baking |
| Music-Genre   | punk         | d&b     | folk    |

