.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-18::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: bike, snowmobile, boat
3 different pets are kept: fish, cat, chinchilla
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: disco, jazz, rock
The people have 3 different jobs:  scientist, fisherman, dressmaker
1. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
2. the scientist is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the fan of rock##1
4. the fan of rock is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
5. the dressmaker is on the right of the fan of disco##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3    |
| Transport      | bike  | snowmobile   | boat  |
| Pet          | cat   | chinchilla | fish   |
| Music-Genre   | jazz      | disco      | rock    |
| Job   | fisherman | scientist    | dressmaker |

