.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-19::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, juice, tea
There are 3 different nationalities: indonesian, spanish, pakistani
There 3 different types of food: garlic, strawberry, kale
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, chaman, blend
1. the person eating strawberry is on the left of the siglo-smoker##1
2. the pakistani is on the left of the chaman-smoker##1
3. the person drinking tea is the siglo-smoker##1
4. the person eating strawberry is the person drinking juice##1
5. the spanish is on the left of the siglo-smoker##1
6. the blend-smoker is on the left of the person eating kale##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |     3      |
| Beverage      | juice         | tea     | coffee     |
| Nationality           | spanish        | pakistani | indonesian |
| Food   | strawberry        | kale   | garlic    |
| Cigar         | blend | siglo   | chaman |

