.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-20::.
House: modern, cottage, colonial
The people have 3 different hobbies: collecting, hiking, traveling
City: venice, edinburgh, miami
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: crime, superhero, mystery
1. the colonial house is on the far left##1
2. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the modern house##1
3. the person traveling to miami is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1
4. the person watching crime movies is on the far left##1
5. the person watching superhero movies is in the middle##1
6. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the person traveling to edinburgh##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3      |
| House          | colonial     | cottage    | modern    |
| Hobby         | collecting | traveling | hiking     |
| City   | venice  | edinburgh      | miami        |
| Movie-Genre         | crime   | superhero   | mystery |

 